        <briefdescription>
<para>Initializes the OpenGL device to access modern OpenGL. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This method must be called **after** the helios application&apos;s `setCurrent()` was called for creating a current context. This OpenGL device will then load from this context.</para>
<para>This method uses the `gladLoadGL` method in conjunction with `glfwGetProcAddress`, which returns the address of the specific OpenGL core.</para>
